detailed_optimizations.code_changes:
示例改动(核心思想)：

1) 预计算常量：
const double stepCap = step / Cap;
const double cRx = stepCap * (1.0/Rx);
const double cRy = stepCap * (1.0/Ry);
const double cRz = stepCap * (1.0/Rz);
const double cC  = stepCap * (-2.0*(1.0/Rx) - 2.0*(1.0/Ry) - (1.0/Rz));
const double cAmb = stepCap * (80.0*(1.0/Rz));

2) 内部区域无分支：
for (int i=1;i<row-1;i++) {
  const int base = i*col;
  const int baseN = (i-1)*col;
  const int baseS = (i+1)*col;
  #pragma omp simd
  for (int j=1;j<col-1;j++) {
    const int idx = base + j;
    const double tC = temp[idx];
    const double tE = temp[idx+1];
    const double tW = temp[idx-1];
    const double tN = temp[baseN+j];
    const double tS = temp[baseS+j];
    const double p  = power[idx];
    // 线性组合，减少括号与重复访存
    const double delta = stepCap*p + cRx*(tE+tW) + cRy*(tN+tS) + cC*tC + cAmb;
    result[idx] = tC + delta;
  }
}

3) 边界单独处理(四条边+四角)，保持正确性但不污染主循环。

空间块：按 i 方向分块，保持三行(temp[i-1],temp[i],temp[i+1])在更高层缓存中复用：
for (int ii=1; ii<row-1; ii+=Bi) {
  int iend = min(ii+Bi, row-1);
  for (int i=ii; i<iend; i++) { ... 内部j循环 ... }
}
并在 i 循环内缓存行指针：
const double* tN = temp + (i-1)*col;
const double* tC = temp + i*col;
const double* tS = temp + (i+1)*col;
double* rC = result + i*col;
const double* pC = power + i*col;

时间阻塞（更难）：一次在小tile上做2+步迭代以减少读写往返，但需要额外halo与更复杂的边界同步。
